WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.280 --> 00:00:01.811
Hey, good morning family!

00:00:01.811 --> 00:00:04.316
I'm excited to be with you all again today.

00:00:04.316 --> 00:00:09.195
I am going to do another 'Pray with Me' video to motivate yourself to pray.

00:00:10.230 --> 00:00:17.293
I'll be praying in English and I'll be praying in tongues.

00:00:27.125 --> 00:00:27.695
I believe corporate prayer is important in these last days, even more than ever before.

00:00:27.695 --> 00:00:35.251
Now is the time we need to pray as a body.

00:00:39.600 --> 00:00:48.370
I believe as we join together in this video, there will be many of you praying for unsaved loved ones and the nation.

00:00:48.370 --> 00:00:52.739
Whatever is on your heart, let's just pray together.

00:00:52.739 --> 00:01:02.104
I'll be leading the prayer by myself; I'm not going to do it with Lynn Hammond in a split screen.

00:01:10.811 --> 00:01:14.752
I'm just going to do it how I pray every day by myself and seek the Lord.

00:01:15.903 --> 00:01:28.559
I'm letting you into my prayer time and we are just going to pray and seek the Father to see what He has for us.

00:01:28.559 --> 00:01:40.064
I hope this helps you jump into the river in your own personal prayer life.

00:01:40.064 --> 00:01:56.293
I'm not saying I'm the greatest prayer warrior, but the Lord told me to do it, so I'm jumping into this river and let's see where it takes us.

00:02:04.782 --> 00:02:08.599
I always start out by singing a song to the Father.

00:02:08.599 --> 00:02:21.720
I enter His courts with thanksgiving and praise, and that's what we're going to do right now.

00:02:23.149 --> 00:02:35.026
Father, we just want to say thank you for all that You've done and all that You're going to do.

00:02:35.026 --> 00:02:42.131
Lord, we worship You and thank You for this day.

00:02:44.951 --> 00:02:48.445
We thank You, Father, for a new day that You've given us.

00:03:03.080 --> 00:03:03.333
This is the day that the Lord has made, and we will rejoice and be glad in it.

00:03:08.813 --> 00:03:21.114
Father, I just want to say thank You for the air that I breathe, for the food that we eat today, and for all that You've provided.

00:03:21.114 --> 00:03:44.100
As we start a new month, I thank You that we're getting ready for September and that You've provided for all the bills for the month of September for every household represented here.

00:03:44.100 --> 00:03:57.879
Whether it is electric, water, gas, phones, or car payments, whatever they have need of, Father, You've provided.

00:04:02.461 --> 00:04:25.417
I thank You, Father, that You are the great provider, the great Jehovah.

00:04:43.222 --> 00:04:44.484
I want to give You praise and glory.

00:04:44.484 --> 00:05:55.990
I'm just going to sing You a song, Father, and I thank You that You said You inhabit the praises of Your people.

00:05:56.000 --> 00:06:24.760
We give You praise and we want to worship You today, Father.

00:06:24.760 --> 00:07:21.120
We honor You and thank You, Lord, that You're so real to us and that there is a heavy presence of Your Spirit on us today.

00:07:21.120 --> 00:07:48.159
We invite You into this day, into our homes, our jobs, and our workplaces.

00:07:48.159 --> 00:08:33.079
Holy Spirit, I thank You that You're going with our children to school today and that You protect them.

00:08:41.000 --> 00:08:50.839
No weapon formed against them shall prosper.

00:08:51.549 --> 00:09:31.272
I plead the blood over our children; no weapon and no devil in hell can come nigh them.

00:09:31.272 --> 00:10:04.150
Not one hair on their heads will be touched by any kind of demonic attack.

00:10:11.518 --> 00:11:03.240
I thank You, Lord, that You are protecting them and that You send Your angels to bear us up in their hands lest we dash our foot against a stone.

00:11:07.852 --> 00:11:35.639
I thank You for Psalm 23 and Psalm 91.

00:11:49.988 --> 00:11:56.550
I give You praise and glory.

00:11:56.560 --> 00:12:29.027
Father, we say: fill my cup, Lord, I lift it up.

00:13:15.440 --> 00:13:15.720
Lord, come and quench this thirsting of my soul.

00:13:15.720 --> 00:13:24.571
Bread of Heaven, feed me till I want no more.

00:13:24.571 --> 00:13:30.897
Fill my cup, fill it up and make me whole.

00:13:30.897 --> 00:13:35.935
It is Jesus.

00:13:39.466 --> 00:13:41.279
We worship You, Holy Spirit.

00:13:41.279 --> 00:13:47.560
You are welcome in this place.

00:13:47.560 --> 00:14:08.865
Omnipotent Father of mercy and grace, Thou art welcome in this place.

00:14:15.399 --> 00:14:36.933
Jesus is coming soon, morning or night or noon.

00:14:36.933 --> 00:15:07.547
Many will meet their doom; trumpets will surely sound.

00:15:07.547 --> 00:16:03.550
All of the dead shall rise, righteous meet in the sky, going where no one dies, Heavenward bound.

00:16:03.560 --> 00:16:18.183
Lord, You're coming so soon.

00:16:18.183 --> 00:16:55.230
Lord, we're so thirsty and we need a fresh touch today.

00:16:55.240 --> 00:17:30.950
Come and quench this thirsting of my soul.

00:17:30.950 --> 00:17:57.440
Bread of Heaven, feed me till I want no more.

00:17:57.440 --> 00:18:26.053
Fill my cup, fill it up and make me whole.

00:18:26.053 --> 00:18:39.825
Amazing Grace, how sweet the sound that saved a wretch like me.

00:18:39.825 --> 00:18:53.320
I once was lost, but now I'm found, was blind but now I see.

00:18:53.320 --> 00:19:04.060
Through many dangers, toils, and snares, I have already come.

00:19:04.060 --> 00:19:17.230
'Tis grace that brought me safe this far, and grace will lead me home.

00:19:17.240 --> 00:19:42.416
When we've been there ten thousand years, bright shining as the sun, we've no less days to sing God's praise than when we first begun.

00:19:44.977 --> 00:20:05.137
Thank You, Father, that even when we mess up the words, You still inhabit the praises of Your people because it's from our hearts.

00:20:05.137 --> 00:20:25.640
Father, we thank You that if we abide in You and Your words abide in us, we shall ask what we will.

00:20:30.000 --> 00:20:34.349
We lift up all the needs of the people today.

00:20:34.349 --> 00:20:52.430
If we make much of the blood, the blood makes much of us.

00:20:52.430 --> 00:20:59.990
What can wash away my sin?

00:20:59.990 --> 00:21:06.005
Nothing but the blood of Jesus.

00:21:06.005 --> 00:21:24.815
Oh, precious is the flow that makes me white as snow; no other fount I know, nothing but the blood of Jesus.

00:21:30.159 --> 00:21:49.154
The blood that gives me strength from day to day will never lose its power, for it reaches to the highest mountain and flows to the lowest valley.

00:21:49.154 --> 00:21:53.095
Glory to the Lamb!

00:22:03.617 --> 00:22:04.586
You are glorious and worthy to be praised.

00:22:04.586 --> 00:22:19.458
You're the Lamb upon the throne, and unto You, we lift our voice in praise.

00:22:29.705 --> 00:22:30.050
Father, we thank You for Your hand on this house.

00:22:45.460 --> 00:22:45.840
We worship You and give You glory right now in Jesus' name.

00:23:05.910 --> 00:23:06.520
Holy Spirit, we invite You now.

00:23:06.520 --> 00:23:22.146
What is on Your heart for us to pray for today?

00:23:25.423 --> 00:23:37.912
We yield ourselves over to the Holy Spirit and thank You that You become so real to us.

00:23:37.912 --> 00:23:59.749
There are so many needs and things pressing that seem overwhelming, but we thank You, Lord, that You are the peace in the midst of the storm.

00:24:12.355 --> 00:24:12.670
You say, 'Peace, be still,' to all storms.

00:24:13.617 --> 00:24:27.586
We call peace to every storm in the lives of every individual here today, in marriages and for children.

00:24:27.586 --> 00:24:42.789
We take authority over you, Satan, and we tell you: thus far and no further!

00:24:42.789 --> 00:24:49.459
Get your hands off of God's property.

00:24:49.459 --> 00:25:02.520
We call those in the storm of life healed, whole, and well in Jesus' name.

00:25:02.520 --> 00:25:14.415
You are the great storm peacemaker; You spoke to the waves and said, 'Peace, be still.

00:25:14.415 --> 00:25:30.287
' We thank You, Lord, that You're the mighty one, the Creator of everything.

00:25:34.090 --> 00:25:38.942
You created us even in our mothers' wombs.

00:25:38.942 --> 00:25:51.530
Every cell and every hair on our head was fearfully and wonderfully made.

00:25:51.530 --> 00:26:10.419
I thank You that we go up higher and higher with You in greater glory and greater manifestations of Your presence.

00:26:15.919 --> 00:26:24.960
We want to be at the spout where the glory comes out, going from glory to glory.

00:26:37.926 --> 00:26:39.640
I thank You, Lord, for the manifestations of that glory in our homes.

00:26:39.640 --> 00:26:47.589
We want to be a vessel that You use in these last days.

00:26:54.649 --> 00:27:09.817
The eyes of the Lord run to and fro throughout the whole earth, looking for a heart whose heart is perfect toward Him.

00:27:09.817 --> 00:27:17.795
Let Your eyes rest upon me today, oh God.

00:27:17.795 --> 00:27:23.680
Create in me a clean heart, oh God.

00:27:31.124 --> 00:27:33.408
You are the Potter and I am the clay; mold me and make me today.

00:27:40.329 --> 00:27:50.364
We have this treasure in earthen vessels, that the excellency of the power would be of You and not of me.

00:27:50.364 --> 00:27:53.600
Holy Spirit, make me more like Jesus.

00:27:54.034 --> 00:28:05.093
We are yielded, filled, and controlled by the Holy Spirit today.

00:28:10.919 --> 00:28:15.720
We are at that river of living water flowing out of the throne.

00:28:15.720 --> 00:28:20.131
We're coming up higher with the fire.

00:28:22.739 --> 00:28:25.580
There are levels of the prophetic and levels of Your presence.

00:28:31.472 --> 00:28:39.512
Father, we yield ourselves to You today so that we would be a light in the darkness and the salt of the earth—the salt that makes people thirsty for You.

00:28:39.512 --> 00:28:49.875
Help us to be the light to somebody today, an answer to prayer in their heart.

00:28:49.875 --> 00:29:00.409
Let Your glory shine on our faces like it did upon Moses.

00:29:00.409 --> 00:29:11.440
Let our shadow pass by like it did the disciples, so that healing flows.

00:29:11.440 --> 00:29:25.662
Even if they touched the shadow, the glory was pouring out so strong that it would heal them.

00:29:25.662 --> 00:29:28.280
Do it again, Lord!

00:29:28.280 --> 00:29:34.770
Do it in us; do it in me.

00:29:34.770 --> 00:29:39.799
Create in us a clean heart, God.

00:29:42.616 --> 00:29:52.739
In these last days, pour out Your Spirit upon us one more time like You did at Azusa Street.

00:29:52.739 --> 00:30:35.938
I thank You, Lord, for the greatest harvest of souls this world has ever seen—a billion-soul harvest that would happen quickly and suddenly in the name of Jesus.

00:30:35.938 --> 00:31:06.310
I call each person watching this video today healed and whole.

00:31:06.320 --> 00:31:21.800
Nothing is too big for You, Lord.

00:31:21.800 --> 00:31:30.165
I call them blessed, healed, and whole mentally, emotionally, physically, and financially.

00:31:30.165 --> 00:31:44.622
I thank You, Father, for healing power that flows on the inside of them, driving out all sickness and disease.

00:31:44.622 --> 00:31:50.724
It's already done, and we receive it.

00:31:50.724 --> 00:32:00.030
Faith calls those things that be not as though they were.

00:32:10.464 --> 00:32:14.193
You paid the price for us to walk in healing.

00:32:18.170 --> 00:32:19.754
Lord, we pray over our finances.

00:32:26.810 --> 00:32:29.341
You said to seek first the kingdom and all these things will be added.

00:32:30.435 --> 00:32:38.306
We seek You today, knowing You know we have every need.

00:32:38.306 --> 00:32:45.390
We seek You, not for the things, but for You.

00:32:45.390 --> 00:32:51.461
We take the care out of our prayer and cast our cares onto You because You care for us.

00:32:51.461 --> 00:33:03.350
If You care for the lily of the field and the sparrow, how much more do You care for us?

00:33:03.350 --> 00:33:12.835
David said he had never seen the righteous forsaken nor his seed begging bread.

00:33:17.803 --> 00:35:15.339
I thank You that we are the righteousness of God in Christ Jesus.

00:35:15.339 --> 00:35:20.057
As we seek You daily, we will find You.

00:35:20.057 --> 00:35:29.127
We knock, and the door is opened to us.

00:36:28.610 --> 00:36:34.347
You have prepared a table before us in the presence of our enemies, and we rest in the finished work of Jesus Christ.

00:36:34.347 --> 00:37:08.427
Great is Your faithfulness to us.

00:37:08.427 --> 00:39:06.075
Morning by morning, new mercies I see; all I have needed Thy hand hath provided.

00:41:14.279 --> 00:41:15.079
Thank You for our unsaved loved ones.

00:41:16.687 --> 00:41:56.230
We send laborers across their path today.

00:41:56.240 --> 00:43:03.419
Some plant, some water, and some bring forth the increase, but we keep the door open by the blood.

00:43:25.444 --> 00:43:25.768
We call them home in Jesus' name.

00:43:34.319 --> 00:43:41.257
One last call—wake up!

00:43:45.820 --> 00:43:51.853
We call them to a fresh touch from Jesus.

00:43:51.853 --> 00:44:08.520
Now, I'm going to pray in tongues and pray perfect prayers out of my spirit.

00:44:08.520 --> 00:44:23.926
I thank You, Holy Spirit, that You move in me and pray perfect prayers that go straight to the throne.

00:44:23.926 --> 00:44:38.339
I'm interceding now over that virus they were talking about, calling forth divine protection over the righteous.

00:44:38.339 --> 00:44:52.815
I'm seeing a wristwatch, a clock that is going backwards, rewinding and giving more time.

00:44:55.359 --> 00:44:56.892
Time is running out.

00:46:09.800 --> 00:46:10.270
The hand of time is coming to an end for this dispensation.

00:48:12.983 --> 00:50:02.570
We are getting ready to step into the Millennial Reign.

00:50:02.570 --> 00:51:22.649
When You showed me the wristwatch and Trump, I wondered if we need to lift him up—that his time is not over.

00:51:22.649 --> 00:51:29.119
Father, bring in one final push, waking up the bride and the church.

00:51:29.119 --> 00:51:39.931
We don't look to a man to save this nation; we look to Jesus.

00:51:47.036 --> 00:51:48.022
It will only be an awakening unto God that will save America.

00:51:57.848 --> 00:51:59.092
I pray a special covering over every individual here, that the plague does not come nigh us.

00:51:59.092 --> 00:52:02.880
No virus in hell can come nigh us.

00:52:02.880 --> 00:52:08.943
We cover ourselves and our families in the blood.

00:52:08.943 --> 00:52:16.460
We are in the peace that passes all understanding concerning our hearts and families.

00:52:16.460 --> 00:52:25.608
We thank You, Lord, that we're always in the right place at the right time.

00:52:25.608 --> 00:52:29.140
Thank you for joining me today.

00:52:30.115 --> 00:52:57.106
I know a lot of you have to get back to work, but I wanted to give a little video of prayer so you could jump in the river and get some encouragement on the way to work.

00:52:57.106 --> 00:53:05.080
If you liked it, give it a thumbs up.

00:53:05.080 --> 00:53:14.262
I'll do more like this if you want to sing or pray more with me.

00:53:15.150 --> 00:53:16.530
It's on my heart.

00:53:29.440 --> 00:53:29.785
I want to pray more about the thing I just saw: Trump's face and that clock.

00:53:29.785 --> 00:53:38.219
It was a wristwatch moving backwards and then forwards to the 15-minute mark.

00:53:38.219 --> 00:53:45.750
It was a short span of time—a delay, but then it moved back.

00:53:45.750 --> 00:53:56.044
It's like He's saying time's up; He gave more time, and now the time is up.

00:54:00.119 --> 00:54:02.040
Jesus is coming, folks, and I hope you all are ready.

00:54:02.040 --> 00:54:09.512
We are going to see a great harvest of souls.

00:54:09.512 --> 00:54:18.839
There is going to be a move of His presence beyond anybody's comprehension.

00:54:18.839 --> 00:54:21.853
It will be a quick work.

00:54:21.853 --> 00:54:32.729
Then we'll be caught up for the seven-year tribulation to be with Him, and then we'll come back down.

00:54:34.020 --> 00:54:37.446
I want you all to be encouraged today.

00:54:37.446 --> 00:54:42.551
Yes, there are dark days, but the light is getting lighter.

00:54:45.069 --> 00:54:49.060
You have authority and are seated with Him in the heavenlies.

00:54:50.140 --> 00:54:54.240
You have nothing to fear as a believer bought with the blood of Jesus.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.550
To be absent from the body is to be present with the Lord.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:05.250
When we die, we go home to see Jesus; we're instantaneously with Him in glory.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:06.650
Jesus has a plan for your life to prosper you and be in health, even as your soul prospers.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.800
There are good days ahead for the believers.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:05.250
If you're new here and never seen me before, God bless you for sticking around.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.900
I'm going to do more videos like this because the Lord told me to.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.200
Put a smile on your face and a song in your heart.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.750
Jesus loves you so much.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.800
God bless you and have a wonderful day.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.400
See you next time.
